01:08:33,810 --> 01:08:38,482
[Horn honking]

1331
01:08:44,288 --> 01:08:45,789
[Engine stops]

1332
01:08:48,758 --> 01:08:50,560
[Car door closes]

1333
01:08:52,562 --> 01:08:54,264
I had to get away
