1349
01:09:51,621 --> 01:09:53,690
Maybe it's not a good idea.
We would...
No, it's not a good idea.

1350
01:09:57,727 --> 01:09:59,729
It's far out, man.

1351
01:09:59,763 --> 01:10:02,932
[Laughs]

1352
