1356
01:10:29,293 --> 01:10:32,362
Linda.
Is your license still good?

1357
01:10:32,396 --> 01:10:33,963
Yeah.

1358
01:10:33,997 --> 01:10:36,666
Then you're driving.

1359
01:10:38,968 --> 01:10:41,037
