1361
01:10:43,807 --> 01:10:45,709
Oh, I know that place.
I've been there.

1362
01:10:45,742 --> 01:10:46,843
Who lives there now?

1363
01:10:46,876 --> 01:10:49,479
Don't matter.
They're rich pigs.

1364
01:10:53,082 --> 01:10:56,986
